2. The Criminal Who Couldn't Do Evil (reprinted from Strange Adventures)

3. The Tribe Beneath the Sea Part 2: the Watery World That Time Forgot Part 3: Duel in the Deep (Tomahawk)

9. The Battle of the Pyramid (Golden Gladiator)
